page.title: 10Buildings
page.content: Most of the Buildings in our block are residential dwellings, there are two schools and a few commerial premises.The houses vary greatly in age size and style.One house is three hundred years old but the majority are between one hundred years to twenty years old.There is only one very recently built area, the houses are only two years old.Most of the houses are brick built,red or brown brick,a few are wooden and only a couple are thatched.There are many large detatched houses with four or more bedrooms.Most is private housing with three areas of council housing.One of the largest buildings is Elvendon priory,a private house which on rare occasions opens to the public
